The '''Norfolk gerygone''' ('''''Gerygone modesta''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Acanthizidae]]. It is [[endemic]] to [[Norfolk Island]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s, subtropical or tropical moist [[shrubland]], and pastureland. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]].

